me-day-beats.jpg\" alt width=\"2002\" height=\"1126\" />\r<br />\n\r<br />\nThere's a big collection of Beats headphones discounted for Prime Day this year, starting with the Beats Studio Buds for <a href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Studio-Cancelling-Earbuds-Built-Bluetooth-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB09VWH36DH%3Fref_%3DOct_DLandingS_D_f9f9cf63_5\"><strong>$89.99</strong></a>, down from $149.95. The newer Beats Studio Buds+ are on sale for <a href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Cancelling-Compatibility-Microphone-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB0C2W1KLSS%3Fref_%3DOct_DLandingS_D_f9f9cf63_17\"><strong>$149.99</strong></a>, down from $169.95.\r<br />\n\r<br />\n<div><a href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdeal%2Ff9f9cf63%3FshowVariations%3Dtrue%26pf_rd_r%3DWAC145HRFEAYV9PNG5GW%26pf_rd_t%3DEvents%26pf_rd_i%3Dprimeday%26pf_rd_p%3D0f855fc7-6931-4ecb-8fd6-0f3434773050%26pf_rd_s%3Dslot-6%26ref%3Ddlx_prime_gd_dcl_tlt_1_f9f9cf63_dt_sl6_50\" target=\"_blank\"><div><div>UP TO 54% OFF</div>Beats Headphones for Prime Day</div></a></div>\r<br />\n\r<br />\nThe Powerbeats Pro are available for <a href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPowerbeats-Pro-Totally-Wireless-Earphones%2Fdp%2FB07R5QD598%3Fref_%3DOct_DLandingS_D_f9f9cf63_13\"><strong>$149.99</strong></a>, down from $249.95 and the Beats Studio3 Headphones are on sale for <a href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Studio3-Wireless-Over%25E2%2580%2591Ear-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB085292V2M\"><strong>$159.99</strong></a>, down from $349.95. Lastly, the Beats Solo3 Headphones are discounted to <a href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=3088&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Solo3-Wireless-Ear-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB07YVYPNRD%3Ftag%3Dmacrumors-20%26ref_%3DOct_DLanding